	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">Review: Halo 2</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Nenjin Darkeyes</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Nov 13, 2004, 01:48</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=Review%3A%20Halo%202&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Freviews%2Farticle_24.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
